snippet.title: ROCKETPULT mini - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Reimagined for Playdate, use the crank to fuel up and launch your rocket, then land on the targets with skill and style!

Launching in December 2024. Please stay tuned!

https://rocketpult.com/mini

CREDITS
This game was made in three months with Glitch City LA by:
Parse (https://parsenoire.com) - Design, Programming, and UI
Lena Huang (https://lenahuang.com) - Art and Animation
Chris Lucca (https://chrislucca.com) - Music and Sound Design
